title: Olympus 02 (of 4) (2009) (c2c) (Minutemen-DTs&Okaza Carlita)
description:
Olympus 02 (of 4) (2009) (c2c) (Minutemen-DTs&Okaza Carlita)
story NATHAN EDMONDSON
art & cover CHRISTIAN WARD

The immortal brothers Castor and Pollux learn that they have unleashed onto Earth a beast long held captive in Hades. As this creature Pelops, aided by the demonic Harpies, murders young women in London and Paris the brothers are sent on separate paths to protect the last two of four sisters before Pelops can reach them first. Issue 2 of OLYMPUS follows darkly the fantastic art and dynamic storytelling realized in Issue 1 by two of the industry's hottest newcomers.
